{"data":[{"date":"15:44 13/08","title":"Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111au l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho, Barcelona \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 Barca t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nasser Al Khelaifi c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. Ch\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Qatar Airways.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Qatar Airways song g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u1ec1n tr\u1edf m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Rakuten c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, Barca \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft o\u00e1n v\u1edbi PSG. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Marco Verratti v\u00e0 Rabiot cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Real m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 Diario Gol c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2n hi\u1ec3m ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa PSG v\u00e0 Real l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Barca-muon-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-30-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Real c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb lung l\u1ea1c. Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, Modric \u0111ang g\u00e2y t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric song Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c chia tay s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu, Los Blancos s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Rabiot t\u1edbi PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-172-194240.html\">HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ai-o-real-madrid-da-khuyen-kovacic-ra-di-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194208.html\">Ai \u1edf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean Kovacic ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chot-eriksen-thay-modric-180-194307.html\">Real Madrid chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/them-mot-tien-dao-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid-180-194385.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2323","checkdouble":"194389"},{"date":"14:57 13/08","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u mai 14/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngang ng\u1eeda Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguyen Thanh Vinh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/2/8/muon-hagl-thua-nhieu-de-kiem-nghiem-ban-linh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh mu\u1ed1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh v\u1eabn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D Pakistan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018. </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra sao, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec BHL \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n r\u1ea5t k\u0129. Th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t sung v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Pakistan so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam:<em> \u201cD\u1eabu sao, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1. </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tri\u1ec3n khai th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Vinh c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018. Song \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0103n \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u th\u00ec h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e0ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan Saddam Hussain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i  m\u1eb7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2322","checkdouble":"194390"},{"date":"17:01 13/08","title":"HLV Emery: \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Juve</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus chi t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u01b0a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Juve, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Real sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Los Blancos. Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Juventus khi l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecd t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay t\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00ednh Ronaldo l\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Real v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Allegri m\u1eebng r\u1ee1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 22 n\u0103m qua, Juventus ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/hlv-juventus-neu-chung-toi-vao-ban-ket-cung-hoan-toan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Scudetto, Coppa Italia v\u00e0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Italia\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sport Italia. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau 5 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u1eafng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea-172-194073.html\">Chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng, t\u1ea1i sao Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Rugani?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay-184-194164.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2321","checkdouble":"194391"},{"date":"16:29 13/08","title":"Real v\u00e0 Barca nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adriano Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Adriano Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rabiot-cua-psg-180-194389.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adriano Rabiot</span>, khi m\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f2n Luka Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Rabiot, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, PSG v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Rabiot\" title=\"tien ve Rabiot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, PSG s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, PSG c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu Barca v\u00e0 Real Madrid th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Rabiot l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Rabiot gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2320","checkdouble":"194392"},{"date":"15:38 13/08","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bi-chu-nha-lam-kho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-lo-san-tap-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng 50 km t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp do n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ngay c\u1ea1nh s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh.</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sutasoma t\u1ea1i Jakarta, Indonesia. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf s\u00e2n ch\u00ednh n\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u00e2n t\u1eadp cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 50 c\u00e2y s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tu-lo-san-tap-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-tai-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ph\u1ee5 ngay c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, lo ng\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i, ph\u1ea3i \u0111i 4-5h \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, BHL Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp s\u00e2n do BTC s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp.\u00a0Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e2n t\u1eadp trong khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung, c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Haper Cikarang kho\u1ea3ng 8km.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec: \"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 chi ph\u00ed. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm, ch\u1ecdn s\u00e2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u01a1n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i 4-5 ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 th\u00ec s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t\".<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 12/8, do b\u1ecb b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed t\u1eadp mu\u1ed9n l\u00fac 20h00 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ee7y bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y v\u00e0 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp chay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00ea-t\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0103n t\u1ed1i, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u nay c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 16h00 \u0111\u1ebfn 17h30 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung, Cikarang. Ng\u00e0y mai (14/8), th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD v\u1edbi Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2319","checkdouble":"194393"},{"date":"16:29 13/08","title":"Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, HLV Juventus n\u1ed5 vang","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Juve</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus chi t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u01b0a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Juve, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Real sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Los Blancos. Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Juventus khi l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecd t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay t\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00ednh Ronaldo l\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Real v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Allegri m\u1eebng r\u1ee1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 22 n\u0103m qua, Juventus ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/hlv-juventus-neu-chung-toi-vao-ban-ket-cung-hoan-toan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Scudetto, Coppa Italia v\u00e0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Italia\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sport Italia. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau 5 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u1eafng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea-172-194073.html\">Chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng, t\u1ea1i sao Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Rugani?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay-184-194164.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2318","checkdouble":"194396"},{"date":"17:01 13/08","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski. Muller tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewandowski t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga, Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia l\u00e0 Eintracht Frankfurt \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00eam qua. Ch\u1ec9 sau 54 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Bayern \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-0. C\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Kingsley Coman v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara ghi 2 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa cho Bayern. Chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u1eafng 5-0 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Commerzbank-Arena c\u1ee7a Frankfurt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski v\u1edbi l\u1eddi khen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Muller tin Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewy</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Lewandowski l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Dortmund h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Qua \u0111\u00f3, Muller hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lewandowski b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span><br>\r\n<span>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1eeb Lewandowski gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd\u201d, Muller n\u00f3i. \u201cAnh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Lewandowski \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao CLB kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c, Jerome Boateng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n sang Paris Saint-Germain. V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, Muller cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Boateng\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sung m\u00e3n, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 anh \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bayern tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng-197-194077.html\">PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic-193-194033.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2317","checkdouble":"194398"},{"date":"17:27 13/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: MU chia tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/chinh-thuc-mu-chia-tay-wilson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o James Wilson t\u1edbi CLB Aberdeen \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>MU chia tay Wilson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Scotland trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Aberdeen. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wilson chia tay MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0 Brighton, Derby County v\u00e0 Sheffield United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U21 Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc Hull City n\u0103m 2014. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 20 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C MU chia tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o James Wilson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C MU chia tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o James Wilson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/chinh-thuc-mu-chia-tay-wilson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU\u00a0chia tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o James Wilson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, Wilson \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Sheffield h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Anh ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, James Wilson s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf Aberdeen. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi sau khi Adam Rooney chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Salford City h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<h2>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Wilson</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. HLV c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Man United l\u00e0 Ricky Sbragia \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Aberdeen. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nghe n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Aberdeen \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Aberdeen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qua \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho t\u00f4i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ecdn Aberdeen b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Scotland \u0111ang d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Aberdeen c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean TV r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u00ecn chung t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski-193-194398.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-se-tro-lai-old-trafford-vao-dau-nam-2019-172-194383.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2316","checkdouble":"194400"},{"date":"17:37 13/08","title":"HLV Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/hlv-real-muon-co-them-2-tan-binh-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid mua th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n Real mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi Los Blancos, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-real-muon-co-them-2-tan-binh-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid mua th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi Karim Benzema, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, HLV Lopetegui c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f2n Luka Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter Milan l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T TBN mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Adrien Rabiot, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-1108-Real-mua-Thiago-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thiago Alcantara l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN. Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, Los Blancos t\u00ednh chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, Edison Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG, Timo Werner c\u1ee7a Leipzig v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111\u00f2i 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Cavani, song h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Werner c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Leipzig h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n Inter kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Icardi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Real Madrid s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. NHM c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2315","checkdouble":"194402"},{"date":"17:51 13/08","title":"Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Man xanh nhanh ch\u00f3ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sterling \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ghi t\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep mu\u1ed1n Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep mu\u1ed1n Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Pep-muon-Man-City-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Raheem-Sterling-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Man xanh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Sterling \u0111\u00e3 ghi m\u1ed9t trong hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Man xanh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Arsenal l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 50 c\u1ee7a Sterling \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Pep Guardiola.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pep mu\u1ed1n Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Man xanh nhanh ch\u00f3ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep mu\u1ed1n Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep mu\u1ed1n Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep mu\u1ed1n Man City gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sterling</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi BL\u0110 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Sterling, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Sterling v\u1edbi Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2020, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, Man xanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u00e9p gi\u00e1 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Real l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Sterling, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, Sterling ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man City l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi m\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 100.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, Man xanh mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng l\u00ean 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n song Sterling \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu gia h\u1ea1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2314","checkdouble":"194403"},{"date":"09:43 13/08","title":"Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i x\u1eed l\u00fd h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 Van Gaal \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-van-dang-phai-xu-ly-hau-qua-van-gaal-de-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf Old Trafford.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</span>. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Jose Mourinho ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o xua b\u1edbt \u00e2u lo sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m \u1edf Old Trafford, v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 3 t\u00e2n binh (2/3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb) v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn c\u0103ng th\u0103ng leo thang v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i chung, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n chi ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng \u00edt sau hai n\u0103m t\u1edbi gi\u1edd ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng MU, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 hai qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB l\u00e0 Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111ang gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Louis Van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-van-dang-phai-xu-ly-hau-qua-van-gaal-de-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf Gary Neville l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1ecf ra c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Mourinho. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCLB \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra kho\u1ea3ng 700 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi Sir Alex Ferguson gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t gia t\u00e0i. N\u1ebfu anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i 6 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eb1ng MU l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 v\u00e0 chi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m ti\u1ebfp theo, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam danh hi\u1ec7u r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Mourinho b\u1ea1o chi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, c\u01a1 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf m\u00ecnh cho nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng Van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i ra sao.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n b\u00e1n \u0111i 7-8-9-10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng theo \u0111\u00fang \u00fd mu\u1ed1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i 15 n\u0103m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u00e1i g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f3t th\u00eam ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m do nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m g\u00e2y n\u00ean \u1edf 2-3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i tin Mourinho b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mang \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ra d\u00e1ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man Utd h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2313","checkdouble":"194375"},{"date":"10:01 13/08","title":"T\u00e1i tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng, Sarri g\u1eedi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \"d\u1ea1y d\u1ed7\" Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/tai-trong-dung-sao-that-sung-sarri-gui-thong-diep-den-tien-nhiem-conte.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mata v\u00e0 Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 12 th\u00e1ng v\u1edbi M.U. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/mu-dam-phan-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-bo-doi-nguoi-tbn.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Mata v\u00e0 Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 12 th\u00e1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Mata ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai th\u00ec Herrera d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Mata \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea. Barca nh\u1eafmAnder Herrera n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U, Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ngay trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU len ke hoach giu chan Mata va Herrera\" title=\"MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mata v\u00e0 Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/herrrera-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mata v\u00e0 Herrera</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Mata v\u00e0 Herrera, song \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mata c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Mata v\u00e0 Herrera v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c M.U \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Marouane Fellaini gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2312","checkdouble":"194376"},{"date":"09:34 13/08","title":"NHM MU ti\u1ebfc \u0111\u1ee9t ru\u1ed9t khi nghe th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/mu-tu-choi-co-hoi-chieu-mo-shaqiri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Xherdan Shaqiri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0o tay Liverpool.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Shaqiri tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Stoke City. Anh ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 42% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Stoke City \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 MU mua Xherdan Shaqiri tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 MU mua Xherdan Shaqiri tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/Tiet-lo-MU-mua-Xherdan-Shaqiri-truoc-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU b\u1ecf qua c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Shaqiri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng Xherdan Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Stoke tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi Stoke c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 13.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Blick, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, song Shaqiri kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 nh\u1eafm Willian, Perisic v\u00e0 Bale, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecd m\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Shaqiri, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n khi\u1ebfn Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Shaqiri k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Xherdan Shaqiri th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i sao v\u00e0o tay Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shaqiri\" title=\"Shaqiri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/huyen-thoai-mu-tiep-tuc-dau-khau-voi-tan-binh-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Shaqiri l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng, v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-mu-klopp-danh-loi-ca-ngoi-cho-1-cai-ten-172-192240.html\" target=\"_blank\">Shaqiri ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi MU </span>trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Mourinho ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng 13.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Shaqiri th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng M.U l\u1ea1i b\u1ecf qua r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nShaqiri l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 ba Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah \u1edf Liverpool. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2311","checkdouble":"194377"},{"date":"10:31 13/08","title":"Gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Barcelona, \"d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1ng sang\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/giai-cuu-barcelona-du-bi-hang-sang-duoc-dam-bao-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Ernesto Valverde t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i Ousmane Dembele sau khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Barcelona v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Sevilla gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Barcelona m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi su\u00f4n s\u1ebb b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/5-diem-nhan-sevilla-12-barca-180-194361.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla</span> th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u00e0o d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd. B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u00fat xa xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c 2-1.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dembele sau tr\u1eadn Barca 2-1 Sevilla h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dembele sau tr\u1eadn Barca 2-1 Sevilla h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/giai-cuu-barcelona-du-bi-hang-sang-duoc-dam-bao-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dembele sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Barca 2-1 Sevilla</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 Barca 2-1 Sevilla, HLV Ernesto Valverde t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Ousmane Dembele v\u00ec c\u00f4ng lao gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n 105 tri\u1ec7u Euro b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i kh\u0103n g\u00f3i ra \u0111i ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dembele: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ebft m\u1ef1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Valverde cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1eadp t\u00e0nh \u00edt bu\u1ed5i trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/13/Sevilla-vs-Barcelona.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2310","checkdouble":"194378"},{"date":"09:44 13/08","title":"MU \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/mu-dam-phan-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-bo-doi-nguoi-tbn.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mata v\u00e0 Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 12 th\u00e1ng v\u1edbi M.U. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd gia h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/mu-dam-phan-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-bo-doi-nguoi-tbn.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Mata v\u00e0 Herrera ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 12 th\u00e1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Mata ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai th\u00ec Herrera d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Mata \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea. Barca nh\u1eafmAnder Herrera n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 25 \u0111\u1ebfn 30 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U, Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juan Mata v\u00e0 Ander Herrera, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ngay trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU len ke hoach giu chan Mata va Herrera\" title=\"MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mata v\u00e0 Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/herrrera-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Mata v\u00e0 Herrera</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDaily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Mata v\u00e0 Herrera, song \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mata c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Mata v\u00e0 Herrera v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c M.U \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Marouane Fellaini gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u1edf tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2309","checkdouble":"194379"}]}